MAking Image Transparent


There are two steps to do that
S-1
// NOT EFFICIENT APPROACH AND SHOULD BE AVOIDED
Wrap your image by opacityWidget

Opacity(opacity: 0.5,
                child: Image.asset(
                  'assets/images/quiz.png',
                  width: 300,
                ),
              ),
              
              
              
              
             Step 2 
             
             //  EFFICIENT APPROACH AND SHOULD BE FOLLOWED
             
             This Approach can be fowwoed with every widget ehich accept color parameter
             use the transparency slider in color menu 
             
             
             its more easy and the best way 
             
             
              Image.asset(
                  'assets/images/quiz.png',
                  width: 300,
                  color: Color.fromARGB(167, 242, 234, 234),
                ),
                
                
                
